criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  generally healthy

          -  age 50~80;

          -  good or corrected vision;

          -  good or corrected hearing

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  motor or cognitively impaired;

          -  outside 50~80 age bracket;

          -  inability to speak English;

          -  history of violence or drug abuse.
